<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965116>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Adults of Siberian Geometrinae. A—Thetidia chlorophyllaria; B—T. smaragdaria; C—Comibaena amoenaria; D—Hemistola intermedia Lectotype; E—Geometra zimmermanni Lectotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965116/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965077>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Wing venation. A—Jodis putata; B—Geometra papilionaria; C—Hemithea aestivaria; D—Chlorissa viridata; E—Holarctias rufinaria; F—Rhodostrophia vibicaria; G—Scopula ornata; H—Timandra rectistrigaria; I—Cyclophora albipunctata. A–D—hindwings; E, F—forewings; G–I—right pair of wings. R veins marked in red, M veins marked in blue, Cu veins marked in green, areole marked in teal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965077/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965112>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Adults of Siberian Archiearinae and Geometrinae. A—Archiearis parthenias; B—A. notha; C—Leucobrephos middendorfii; D—Geometra papilionaria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965112/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965125>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Adults of Siberian Geometrinae. A—Hemithea aestivaria; B—Dyschloropsis impararia; C—Chlorissa viridata; D—C. obliterata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965081>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Morphological structures of male abdomen. A—Holarctias rufinaria; B—Scopula ternata; C—S. nigropunctata; D—S. incanata; E—Chlorissa obliterata. A, B, C—genital segment; D—sternite A8; E—basal sternites of abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965081/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

